data.name: lblRule1.Text
data.value: 1. Exam taker should take exam between effective time and time.

data.name: lblRule4.Text
data.value: 3. Please do not leave the take exam page or close browser without hand in paper.

data.name: lblRule5.Text
data.value: 4. If exam taker do not hand in pager, system will hand in pager automatically when time out.

data.name: lblRule6.Text
data.value: 5. Exam taker can not take this exam again after hand in pager.

data.name: lblRule2.Text
